block title
  title 快速入门

block content

  .container.df-container.theme-showcase(role='main')
    // Main jumbotron for a primary marketing message or call to action
    .jumbotron
      .row
        div.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-4
          h1 百度通告!
          p
          p
          p.df-intro
            | 百度通告平台是一款即时消息推送类产品，它旨在通过语音电话、短信、邮件、百度Hi及第三方社交、通讯类渠道保证对消息及时、准确、无遗漏地传送。并基于多种渠道构建运维事件管理、报警升级、通告群发、轮值和验证码等应用与服务。
          .df-icon
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-phone-alt
            span.glyphicon-class &nbsp;&nbsp;电话通告
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-ok.pull-right
          .df-icon
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-comment
            span.glyphicon-class &nbsp;&nbsp;短信通告
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-ok.pull-right
          .df-icon
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-envelope
            span.glyphicon-class &nbsp;&nbsp;邮件通告
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-ok.pull-right
          .df-icon
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-export
            span.glyphicon-class &nbsp;&nbsp;通告升级
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-ok.pull-right
          .df-icon
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-send
            span.glyphicon-class &nbsp;&nbsp;通告群发
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-ok.pull-right
          .df-icon
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-tasks
            span.glyphicon-class &nbsp;&nbsp;事件管理
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-ok.pull-right
          .df-icon
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-calendar
            span.glyphicon-class &nbsp;&nbsp;轮值服务
          .df-icon  
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-repeat
            span.glyphicon-class &nbsp;&nbsp;验证码服务
            
          p(style="margin-top:20px;")
            a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-6.col-lg-12(href='http://tonggao.baidu.com', role='button') 点击进入 »
        div.col-lg-8
          div(style='text-align:center')
            object#reader(width='575', height='500', align='right', codebase='http://fpdownload.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,0,0', classid='clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000')
